    • removeVertex

      public T removeVertex(T v)
      Method to remove vertex from incidence matrix. this.incMatrix[v][i] = -2, where i in [0, nedges). In other words, incMatrix[v][i] == -2 if and only if v is removed vertex.
      Parameters:
      v - Vertex to remove.
      Returns:
      Removed vertex.
